INFORMATION

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

CHANGES

* Version 2.7.0 (2020-12-31)
C: Add support for FreeBSD 12.2-RELEASE
C: Drop support for FreeBSD 12.1-RELEASE

* Version 2.6.0 (2019-11-08)
C: Add support for FreeBSD 12.1-RELEASE
C: Drop support for FreeBSD 12.0-RELEASE

* Version 2.5.0 (2019-05-26)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.8

* Version 2.4.0 (2019-01-13)
C: Add support for FreeBSD 12.0-RELEASE
C: Drop support for FreeBSD 11.2-RELEASE

* Version 2.3.1 (2018-10-20)
E: Update support information of OpenBSD

* Version 2.3.0 (2018-07-01)
C: Add support for FreeBSD 11.2-RELEASE
C: Drop support for FreeBSD 11.1-RELEASE

* Version 2.2.0 (2018-05-22)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.5

* Version 2.1.1 (2018-04-04)
E: Update support information of OpenBSD

* Version 2.1.0 (2018-03-30)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.4

* Version 2.0.0 (2018-02-20)
E: Simplify and improve Ansible role

* Version 1.1.1 (2017-10-18)
E: Update support information of OpenBSD

* Version 1.0.0 (2017-09-04)
F: Initial release
